  "body": "- [x] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n## Link to the project\r\n[Blockchain shop](https://github.com/MarekDzw/Blockchain-Shop)\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nAfter adding \r\n```ts\r\ndeclare let require: any;\r\nconst contract = require('@truffle/contract');\r\n```\r\nin Angular 12 component I get errors in terminal and project want start.\r\nErrors:\r\n```bash\r\n./node_modules/@truffle/compile-common/dist/src/profiler/updated.js:33:24-37 - Error: Module not found: Error: Can't resolve 'fs' in 'C:\\Repositories\\blockchain-shop\\node_modules\\@truffle\\compile-common\\dist\\src\\profiler'\r\n\r\n./node_modules/fs.realpath/index.js:8:9-22 - Error: Module not found:\r\nError: Can't resolve 'fs' in 'C:\\Repositories\\blockchain-shop\\node_modules\\fs.realpath'\r\n\r\n./node_modules/fs.realpath/old.js:24:9-22 - Error: Module not found: \r\nError: Can't resolve 'fs' in 'C:\\Repositories\\blockchain-shop\\node_modules\\fs.realpath'\r\n\r\n./node_modules/glob/glob.js:43:9-22 - Error: Module not found: \r\nError: Can't resolve 'fs' in 'C:\\Repositories\\blockchain-shop\\node_modules\\glob'\r\n\r\n./node_modules/glob/sync.js:4:9-22 - Error: Module not found: \r\nError: Can't resolve 'fs' in 'C:\\Repositories\\blockchain-shop\\node_modules\\glob'\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nAdd below line in any Angular 12 component\r\n```ts \r\nconst contract = require('@truffle/contract'); \r\n```\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nWorking lib where I can use `contract` object in project.\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nErrors in terminal: \r\n```bash\r\n./node_modules/@truffle/compile-common/dist/src/profiler/updated.js:33:24-37 - Error: Module not found: Error: Can't resolve 'fs' in 'C:\\Repositories\\blockchain-shop\\node_modules\\@truffle\\compile-common\\dist\\src\\profiler'\r\n\r\n./node_modules/fs.realpath/index.js:8:9-22 - Error: Module not found:\r\nError: Can't resolve 'fs' in 'C:\\Repositories\\blockchain-shop\\node_modules\\fs.realpath'\r\n\r\n./node_modules/fs.realpath/old.js:24:9-22 - Error: Module not found: \r\nError: Can't resolve 'fs' in 'C:\\Repositories\\blockchain-shop\\node_modules\\fs.realpath'\r\n\r\n./node_modules/glob/glob.js:43:9-22 - Error: Module not found: \r\nError: Can't resolve 'fs' in 'C:\\Repositories\\blockchain-shop\\node_modules\\glob'\r\n\r\n./node_modules/glob/sync.js:4:9-22 - Error: Module not found: \r\nError: Can't resolve 'fs' in 'C:\\Repositories\\blockchain-shop\\node_modules\\glob'\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: ` Win 10 `\r\n* Ethereum client: ` Metamask `\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): `  v5.4.9 (core: 5.4.9) `\r\n* node version (`node --version`): `  v14.17.5 `\r\n* npm version (`npm --version`):  ` 7.20.5  `\r\n",
